[{"Code":"en","Title":"Landbank Online Banking","Slug":"landbank-online-banking","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"5e2404f9-ec49-4551-8cdd-ec7ba26853a9\"><img data-block-id=\"049fa388-1313-4f27-9171-a463e9c79c5d\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/images (1).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"190\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:190px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"2a59da1b-8e30-40f0-abde-d74eadba8f03\">The Land Bank of the Philippines (LANDBANK) is a government-owned bank that serves as one of the country’s largest financial institutions. It is trusted by millions of Filipinos, including government employees, small businesses, farmers, and private individuals. LANDBANK offers a robust online banking platform called <strong>LANDBANK iAccess</strong> for retail banking and <strong>WeAccess</strong> for corporate banking.</p><p data-block-id=\"44bb461c-4581-4a51-b7a3-26355a5100b7\">LANDBANK Online Banking allows users to perform a wide range of financial transactions, including fund transfers, bill payments, and account management, anytime and anywhere. Its accessibility and strong commitment to security make it a preferred platform for individuals and businesses looking for convenience in managing their finances.</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"6146dcc6-4245-4158-a034-de0971f8c50b\">Features</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"926\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\";max-width:926px;width:926px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:463px;\"><col style=\"width:463px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"402452f7-7a96-45f3-8