m;\"><p data-block-id=\"55cbaf83-ec18-4147-8950-585e0c4aaba7\">Multiple Partial Refund</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"957d2006-c589-4751-a1a0-174321a498e2\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"3795b679-c38a-4fae-88f4-7a3498c5b08e\">Refund Validity (days)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"9f5634ea-ac19-47ae-9a88-b4b2d4a3d107\">N/A</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"d1760170-fa28-4c8b-b533-419100be3192\">Compatible integration</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"60823a34-d1b1-427e-90ab-60a877255f19\">Payment API, Payment Link</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"2b081c08-ffd2-493a-b253-c4931f5f1c75\">Payment flow</h2><ul data-block-id=\"87e150ea-d71b-4e40-805e-37f955bc4810\"><li data-block-id=\"181c2d2a-6bc1-4209-a3fb-e13e8dd48e77\"><p data-block-id=\"078e1e91-d284-47a0-a29a-426ce92c9228\">Dekstop QR Flow</p><p data-block-id=\"2d2d0c92-9a2a-44f4-b24d-8935f1b5c147\">&lt;put your video and screenshot&gt;</p></li><li data-block-id=\"6a83948a-6dd9-4373-acc8-1ec7ac527112\"><p data-block-id=\"f80c34a6-7003-4f04-b4bc-b55ce4f84da4\">Redirection</p><p data-block-id=\"ab746d61-9884-4a77-9707-3c45e7466808\">&lt;put your video and screenshot&gt;</p></li><li data-block-id=\"d48ec69a-d382-4ca9-8b77-c05727a2fafe\"><p data-block-id=\"39e9bdca-ba9b-4df1-8360-90ba1e6bc862\">Deeplink (H5)</p><p data-block-id=\"32f3df61-ab83-4f4c-bc2a-111ababeda16\">&lt;put your video and screenshot&gt;</p></li><li data-block-id=\"63fd7739-70c9-438d-b0d2-3a7d79310203\"><p data-block-id=\"3d009435-05e1-4dd0-8e3d-8c38c7e5ca76\">Push Notification</p><p data-block-id=\"3defe89e-0791-4760-80ef-6058d12d4775\">&lt;put your video and screenshot&gt;</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"7cacbff0-6097-4577-8bea-2670eefceb05\"></h2><p data-block-id=\"3a86b5ec-38da-4400-83d2-ef1024cbe6c9\"></p><p data-block-id=\"12295416-ce37-4b1f-ae9c-e422707d5254\"></p><p data-block-id=\"8e9aac87-b7ff-4f0e-b9c9-0178d8f76e42\"></p><p data-block-id=\"1fba7422-3f0f-475f-a3cd-ed72e33bce4f\"></p><p data-block-id=\"acd97665-43b1-498b-89ca-e66b24c0a68f\"></p><p data-block-id=\"490a489a-2a58-4dc9-96ea-9e5cc09fc8be\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Landbank Online Banking","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Landbank Perbankan Online","Slug":"payment-channel-page-pull-11","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"5e2404f9-ec49-4551-8cdd-ec7ba26853a9\"><img data-block-id=\"049fa388-1313-4f27-9171-a463e9c79c5d\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/images (1).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"190\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:190px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"2a59da1b-8e30-40f0-abde-d74eadba8f03\">Land Bank of the Philippines (LANDBANK) adalah bank milik pemerintah yang berfungsi sebagai salah satu lembaga keuangan terbesar di negara itu. Bank ini dipercaya oleh jutaan orang Filipina, termasuk pegawai pemerintah, usaha kecil, petani, dan perorangan. LANDBANK menawarkan platform perbankan online yang kuat bernama <strong>LANDBANK iAccess</strong> untuk perbankan ritel dan <strong>WeAccess</strong> untuk perbankan korporat.</p><p data-block-id=\"44bb461c-4581-4a51-b7a3-26355a5100b7\">LANDBANK Online Banking memungkinkan pengguna untuk melakukan berbagai transaksi keuangan, termasuk transfer dana, pembayaran tagihan, dan manajemen akun, kapan saja dan di mana saja. Aksesibilitasnya dan komitmen yang kuat terhadap keamanan menjadikannya platform pilihan bagi individu dan bisnis yang mencari kemudahan dalam mengelola keuangan mereka.</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"6146dcc6-4245-4158-a034-de0971f8c50b\">Fitur</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"926\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\";max-width:926px;width:926px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:463px;\"><col style=\"width:463px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"402452f7-7a96-45f3-856a-beec3466fb7a\">Kode Channel</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"8de964e4-a637-4b69-b850-7a35c26c8ed9\">LANDBANK_ONLINE_BANKING</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"e924926f-9906-4496-af4a-b319c2a2c8d4\">Mata Uang</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"89cc4585-3036-4f0a-847a-3a0f634c0a27\">PHP</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"6598736d-d850-48ae-b29e-ba649fb13157\">Jumlah Mini